ider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="1PLoBEcM6Y"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/uruha-rushia-may-have-sent-a-message-or-a-thanks-video-to-a-specific-listener-it-is-unknown-whether-this-is-a-violation-of-contract-cancellation-reasons/">Lucia Junha是否向特定观众发送了消息或感谢视频？目前尚不清楚这是否违反了合同取消的原因。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Rushia Junha向特定观众发送了消息和感谢视频。目前尚不清楚这是否违反了合同取消的原因” - P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/uruha-rushia-may-have-sent-a-message-or-a-thanks-video-to-a-specific-listener-it-is-unknown-whether-this-is-a-violation-of-contract-cancellation-reasons/embed/#?secret=Wtk88tnorz#?secret=1PLoBEcM6Y" data-secret="1PLoBEcM6Y" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><div class="uxxia65a88657262ee" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
